page.title: 16Landscape deptford
page.content: The one kilometre square that we are looking at doesn,t have much grass in it, apart from the obvious ; people,s back gardens, thats square if they have any. the landscape of our square is mainly full of houses shops and a couple of industrial places .In my view the main part of our square is probably the hospital.The main part of the area is on the side of a hill. the roads where all the shops are Trafalger road and woolwich road are fairly grotty and grimy with the fumes from the power station and other nealy places with chimneys.
